{
  "stem": "19969.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In all the testimony, the 42nd never mentioned her presence, although they made one slip-up that I found.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In their division journal, I found that she had reported to their headquarters that morning.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's the only reference to her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was, I say, a slip-up, I think, on their part.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They didn't recall recording that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But it's in here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Anyway, they never mentioned-- any of the men from the 42nd division never mentioned that she was with General Linden.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he never mentioned it at all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She mentioned it, of course, in a press dispatches.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And it's been recorded as a book I have here, in which she states that she was in there with the 42nd.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "What I discovered was that General Linden came up there with a small party, maybe 12, 14 men, something like that, mostly officers, and jeep drivers, and a few other enlisted, and I think an interpreter.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he sent a couple of his officers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they went in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they didn't say anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Because my men were quite a distance away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Well, they heard the firing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they came back said, well, we don't see anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Well, they came in the main gate to the, the whole area, which is only two blocks from the prison compound.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So they-- there was, according to General Linden, there was a couple of people who met him at the gate.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He said one was a Red Cross representative.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I've never figured that out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I don't think the Germans allowed any Red Cross people in the concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But I suspect it was a Gestapo man who put on a Red Cross band and said he was Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Because I'm certain the Germans did not allow the Red Cross into those concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
